---
import RegionSection from "./RegionSection.astro";
---

<RegionSection

    title="Major Landmarks"

    subtitle="Places that have shaped Solmara's history and legend."

>

<div class="landmark-grid">

    <article class="landmark-card">

        <h3>The Tree of Gods</h3>

        <p>

            A colossal ancient oak overlooking the Great Lake,
            revered throughout Solmara as one of the oldest living
            landmarks in Eldoria.

        </p>

    </article>

    <article class="landmark-card">

        <h3>The Crown Road</h3>

        <p>

            The oldest highway in Solmara connecting the region's
            three great kingdoms.

        </p>

    </article>

    <article class="landmark-card">

        <h3>Manicallus Basin</h3>

        <p>

            Beneath the Great Lake lies the largest known concentration
            of Manicallus crystals in Eldoria.

        </p>

    </article>

    <article class="landmark-card">

        <h3>Solaris Mountain Range</h3>

        <p>

            Towering mountains protecting Solmara's eastern coast
            from the powerful ocean winds.

        </p>

    </article>

    <article class="landmark-card">

        <h3>Nyxara's Rock</h3>

        <p>

            A floating stone suspended high above Solmara, said to be
            where Nyxara spends eternity reading the works of mortals.

        </p>

    </article>

</div>

</RegionSection>

<style>

.landmark-grid{

    display:grid;

    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(320px,1fr));

    gap:2rem;

}

.landmark-card{

    padding:2.5rem;

    border-radius:22px;

    border:1px solid rgba(198,166,107,.15);

    background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);

    transition:.35s;

}

.landmark-card:hover{

    transform:translateY(-8px);

    border-color:var(--primary);

    box-shadow:

        0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.3),

        0 0 30px rgba(198,166,107,.08);

}

.landmark-card h3{

    font-family:"Cinzel",serif;

    color:var(--text);

    margin-bottom:1rem;

    font-size:2rem;

}

.landmark-card p{

    color:var(--muted);

    line-height:1.9;

}

</style>